00:12:45.720 --> 00:12:47.020
&gt;&gt; Zuri Kenyatte: Okay.

00:12:47.020 --> 00:12:48.440
So have you ever considered

00:12:48.440 --> 00:12:52.200
that one bad decision could
change your life forever?

00:12:52.200 --> 00:12:54.090
The book "Lucky Broken Girl"

00:12:54.090 --> 00:12:56.220
by Ruth Behar taught
me this lesson.

00:12:56.220 --> 00:13:00.510
In the book, an immigrant
Jewish family is involved

00:13:00.510 --> 00:13:03.090
in a car accident and
the daughter Ruthie is

00:13:03.090 --> 00:13:04.720
severely injured.

00:13:04.720 --> 00:13:08.310
Bedridden, Ruthie is
forced to stay in her room,

00:13:08.310 --> 00:13:11.870
strung to the ceiling in
a body cast for a year.

00:13:11.870 --> 00:13:15.020
She is dependent on
her mom for everything,

00:13:15.020 --> 00:13:19.630
even every day necessities like
using the bathroom and bathing.

00:13:19.630 --> 00:13:24.000
Even her meals, which had
to be smaller than usual

00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:28.210
so she would not outgrow her
body cast, are brought to her.

00:13:28.210 --> 00:13:32.280
She is no longer physically
able to go to school,

00:13:32.280 --> 00:13:37.340
so the school sends a tutor
to her house to help her keep

00:13:37.340 --> 00:13:39.140
up with her classwork.

00:13:39.140 --> 00:13:41.800
Life for 10-year-old
Ruthie has changed,

00:13:41.800 --> 00:13:44.440
and there isn't much
she could do about it.

00:13:44.440 --> 00:13:48.660
This book has many morals and
lessons that stuck with me long

00:13:48.660 --> 00:13:50.740
after I finished reading.

00:13:50.740 --> 00:13:52.830
The one that had the
greatest impact is

00:13:52.830 --> 00:13:55.950
that one bad decision could
change a person's life.

00:13:55.950 --> 00:13:58.650
The boys who injured
Ruthie chose to be reckless

00:13:58.650 --> 00:14:01.400
and drive drunk, without
considering the lives

00:14:01.400 --> 00:14:03.090
of others on the road.

00:14:03.090 --> 00:14:06.920
As a result, they not only
severely wounded Ruthie,

00:14:06.920 --> 00:14:09.730
but they killed other
drivers and themselves.

00:14:09.730 --> 00:14:11.930
This one poor choice
changed a community

00:14:11.930 --> 00:14:13.850
of people's lives forever.

00:14:13.850 --> 00:14:16.670
A woman is paralyzed for
the rest of her life,

00:14:16.670 --> 00:14:20.260
Ruthie loses her independence
and is disabled for a year,

00:14:20.260 --> 00:14:23.880
and the boys don't get to
see the other side of 16.

00:14:23.880 --> 00:14:27.320
This had a life-long
effect on the families too.

00:14:27.320 --> 00:14:30.810
This is tragic, something I
would never want to experience.

00:14:30.810 --> 00:14:34.660
"Lucky Broken Girl" taught me
to think about the consequences

00:14:34.660 --> 00:14:36.920
of my actions before doing them.

00:14:36.920 --> 00:14:38.510
This book also encouraged me

00:14:38.510 --> 00:14:41.650
to find a new perspective
when I'm feeling sad.

00:14:41.650 --> 00:14:44.270
When Ruthie is depressed
and starts painting the boys

00:14:44.270 --> 00:14:47.830
as ghosts, her new neighbor,
Chico, turned her bed

00:14:47.830 --> 00:14:51.110
around towards the window to
give her an optimistic view.

00:14:51.110 --> 00:14:53.690
Ruthie begins to feel
better instantly.

00:14:53.690 --> 00:14:56.490
Instead of being preoccupied
with negative thoughts,

00:14:56.490 --> 00:14:59.320
she starts painting
butterflies and flowers.

00:14:59.320 --> 00:15:02.170
This taught me that sometimes
all it takes is a different

00:15:02.170 --> 00:15:04.850
point of view to
change the scenario.

00:15:04.850 --> 00:15:07.310
"Lucky Broken Girl" taught
me that I am in control.

00:15:07.310 --> 00:15:11.510
I have the power to determine
my actions and my life.

00:15:11.510 --> 00:15:17.180
[ Applause ]

00:15:17.180 --> 00:15:18.560
&gt;&gt; Jamie Uphold:
Congratulations, Zuri.

00:15:18.560 --> 00:15:21.950
You can certainly see why
she's our third place winner.

00:15:21.950 --> 00:15:26.010
I love her comment about one
choice can alter the lives

00:15:26.010 --> 00:15:28.520
of a whole community.

00:15:28.520 --> 00:15:30.070
Great job, Zuri.

00:15:30.070 --> 00:15:33.740
Next up, I'm happy to
