00:20:45.730 --> 00:20:47.480
&gt;&gt; Tyler Williams: Dear
librarian, let me tell you

00:20:47.480 --> 00:20:49.920
about how the Harry Potter
series gave me the strength

00:20:49.920 --> 00:20:51.220
to be happy again.

00:20:51.220 --> 00:20:54.220
A few years ago I was bullied
in school by my best friends,

00:20:54.220 --> 00:20:56.300
and I was too afraid
to tell an adult.

00:20:56.300 --> 00:20:58.080
I eventually told
my parents about it

00:20:58.080 --> 00:20:59.540
and the threat was gone.

00:20:59.540 --> 00:21:01.590
It's a well-known
fact among Potterheads

00:21:01.590 --> 00:21:03.870
that Harry Potter
overcame Voldemort.

00:21:03.870 --> 00:21:06.790
I kind of thought of it like
this; Harry as the schoolboy

00:21:06.790 --> 00:21:08.680
and Voldemort as the bully.

00:21:08.680 --> 00:21:11.800
Harry overcame Voldemort
and became a hero.

00:21:12.860 --> 00:21:15.110
Albus Dumbledore said in
the book "Harry Potter

00:21:15.110 --> 00:21:17.940
and the Sorcerer's Stone, It
takes a great deal of bravery

00:21:17.940 --> 00:21:19.970
to stand up to our
enemies, but just as much

00:21:19.970 --> 00:21:21.640
to stand up to our friends."

00:21:21.640 --> 00:21:24.160
I can relate to this quote
because my bully pretended

00:21:24.160 --> 00:21:26.560
to be my friends by
playing games with me

00:21:26.560 --> 00:21:28.710
and letting me come
over for a sleepover

00:21:28.710 --> 00:21:30.740
but he was a wolf
in sheep's clothing.

00:21:30.740 --> 00:21:33.640
The way I was treated
left me in the darkness.

00:21:33.640 --> 00:21:35.450
Dumbledore in "Harry
Potter and the Prisoner

00:21:35.450 --> 00:21:38.760
of Azkaban" also said,
"Happiness can be found even

00:21:38.760 --> 00:21:41.180
in the darkest of times
if one only remembers

00:21:41.180 --> 00:21:42.590
to turn on the light."

00:21:42.590 --> 00:21:44.080
I needed to get out of the dark,

00:21:44.080 --> 00:21:46.650
so I turned on the light
and told my parents.

00:21:46.650 --> 00:21:49.330
I was happy again because
I was free from my bully.

00:21:49.330 --> 00:21:50.630
By defeating the threat,

00:21:50.630 --> 00:21:53.240
I made sure that other
kids didn't share my fate.

00:21:53.240 --> 00:21:55.110
The Harry Potter series
helped me find light

00:21:55.110 --> 00:21:56.860
in my darkest of times.

00:21:56.860 --> 00:21:59.040
It gave me courage to
overcome a bully just

00:21:59.040 --> 00:22:00.920
like Harry defeated Voldemort.

00:22:00.920 --> 00:22:03.600
My hope is that other kids get
the same courage I did while

00:22:03.600 --> 00:22:07.240
reading this amazing series.

